lyrics:
Walkin' down the street, got a craving so sweet,
Wendy's in mind, a treat I wanna meet.
Fresh beef on the grill, makes my heart thrill,
Square burgers, frosty chills, in my stomach, fill.

(Chorus)
Red hair, bright smile, in style for a while,
Wendy's, you've got that flair, makes my taste buds go wild.
